{"tid":1275961,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[AMD Yes!] 利用半導體製冷，AMD 新 3D 堆疊專利有望解決 CPU 散熱問題！","createTime":"2019-07-02T00:32:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T04:46:17.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e0b096819bf99775e1413ee2d7026aeacf5138f7","tid":1275961,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T00:32:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hkepc.com/18106/CPU_都轉向_3D_堆疊利用半導體製冷_AMD_新_3D_堆疊專利有望解決散熱問題\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkepc.com%2F18106%2FCPU_%E9%83%BD%E8%BD%89%E5%90%91_3D_%E5%A0%86%E7%96%8A%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E5%8D%8A%E5%B0%8E%E9%AB%94%E8%A3%BD%E5%86%B7_AMD_%E6%96%B0_3D_%E5%A0%86%E7%96%8A%E5%B0%88%E5%88%A9%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%9B%E8%A7%A3%E6%B1%BA%E6%95%A3%E7%86%B1%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C&d=9Ou39NWu4C7Ce3sh0Mn9C7TKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=2c3cde29\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkepc.com/18106/CPU_都轉向_3D_堆疊利用半導體製冷_AMD_新_3D_堆疊專利有望解決散熱問題</a><br />\n<br />\n隨著半導體製程工藝的升級難度越來越大，進度越來越緩慢，台積電的 7nm 工藝開發成本已經超過了 30 億美元，接下來的 5nm 工藝預計要超過 50 億美元，在平面上想提升晶體管密度這事情已經變得相當有挑戰性，3D 堆疊工藝可能是解決這問題的一個好方法，結構簡單的 NAND Flash 已經大面積轉向 3D 堆疊工藝了，HBM 記憶體也是利用 3D 堆疊工藝生產的，但是 3D 堆疊工藝也不是萬能的，散熱就是 3D 堆疊工藝要面臨的一大難題，層數越多熱量堆積就越嚴重，AMD 近日申請的一項專利就有可能解決這一問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://file1.hkepc.net/2019/07/source/01155907471933414753.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffile1.hkepc.net%2F2019%2F07%2Fsource%2F01155907471933414753.jpg&h=b2843e14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">CPU 也要上 3D 堆疊工藝了，這是 Intel 採用 Foveros 3D 封裝工藝所生產的 Lakefield SoC。</span></div><br />\n<br />\nAMD 這一專利的就是在 3D 堆疊記憶體的邏輯層和儲存層之間插入一片 TEC 熱點效應散熱模組，也就是我們所說的半導體製冷器或溫差製冷器，它利用 Peltier Effect 珀爾帖效應，由 N 、P 型材料組成一對熱電偶，當熱電偶通入直流電流後，因直流電通入的方向不同，將在電偶結點處產生吸熱和放熱現象<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"b577ac7cd70b79cfaf9899151aaa35c65b1f0531","tid":1275961,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T00:33:45.000Z","msg":"而這個現像是可以根據電流的方向而反轉的，也就是說可以根據傳感器反饋的結果，都可以利用熱電偶把熱量從較高的那一端轉移到溫度較低的一端，讓熱量分佈更為平均，這一專利在任何 3D 堆疊生產的芯片上都相當實用，然而這一過程是會產生額外的發熱的，也會帶來額外的功耗，所以這一專利是否真的有用我們還得等實際產品出來再說。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://file1.hkepc.net/2019/07/source/01155909491853473247.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffile1.hkepc.net%2F2019%2F07%2Fsource%2F01155909491853473247.jpg&h=8ddd4307&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://file1.hkepc.net/2019/07/source/01155908481697685915.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffile1.hkepc.net%2F2019%2F07%2Fsource%2F01155908481697685915.jpg&h=711c4748&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f8767b4f978a74a3b9860862b7d3eac3e07230bb","tid":1275961,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T00:38:24.000Z","msg":"咪L玩<br />\n將cpu放喺最頂層再直接用焊料散走好過"},{"pid":"7d0ee0b299ebdcfc7453ab7ec70b4fcdeda6ac45","tid":1275961,"uid":239558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:37:15.000Z","msg":"半導體 一邊凍一邊熱<br />\n好危險"},{"pid":"d0e3e4798e1023fe65de5bc79dda9b70e8c28acb","tid":1275961,"uid":42586,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:43:44.000Z","msg":"幾年前仲比人笑緊幾粒core 痴埋一齊扮multicore<br />\n而家打到intel 落花流水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f3f0a5b6c1e61a1093b8ab9f95f1f0c063982da","tid":1275961,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0e3e4798e1023fe65de5bc79dda9b70e8c28acb","tid":1275961,"uid":42586,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:43:44.000Z","msg":"幾年前仲比人笑緊幾粒core 痴埋一齊扮multicore<br />\n而家打到intel 落花流水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:46:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}